item.title: BOT vs Bots
item.author: bradinrohde0@gmail.com (Bradin Rohde)
item.description: The Cybersecurity Club’s collaboration event with the Baddies of Tech Club. We taught beginner cybersecurity topics, introduced some common website vulnerabilities, and exploited a few of them by hacking robots.
